  "description": "Standardize CLI countable resource command groups to canonical plural forms (changes, specs, archives, drafts) while maintaining singular aliases for backward compatibility. This change includes a new governing policy spec (cli:cli/command-resource-naming), updates to affected CLI specs, and comprehensive updates to documentation and skill examples to ensure a consistent command vocabulary across the ecosystem.",
